# Placeholder file for authentication BLoCs

This directory will contain BLoC files for state management:
- auth_bloc.dart: Main authentication BLoC
- auth_event.dart: Authentication events
- auth_state.dart: Authentication states
- login_bloc.dart: Login-specific BLoC
- registration_bloc.dart: Registration BLoC
- password_recovery_bloc.dart: Password recovery BLoC

BLoCs handle business logic in the presentation layer.
